channel.title: Weird Portforward problem
channel.description:
Hello well I'm portforwarding with Utorrent and I have a problem, I've been able to portforward my server with Utorrent many times before, But now it's not working, like if my servers not running then i enter Port 43594 in my preferences>Connections then apply and save while my server isn't open I check on Canyouseeme.org, and it says "Success"
But while my server is running I run my server then open Utorrent then I make sure it's working right, then check and it says "Error" Please help me.
